behavior and technological advances to global market dynamics, these insights reveal how companies are navigating an evolving economic landscape. Below are three</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742456-q3-24-earnings-insights-consumer-resilience-ai-advancements-and-supply-chain-shifts", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:56:58"}, {"id": "4742459", "title": "Super Micro Computer: Measuring The Risks, Hold For Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman using tape measure with risk wording for risk analysis investigate management and assessment concept.\" data-id=\"2150553576\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"822px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dilok Klaisataporn</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The bulls came rampaging back in pre-market trading on December 2nd, 2024 as Super Micro Computer (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>) issued a press release that the independent review of its internal controls, operations, and accounting practices <a href=\"https://ir.supermicro.com/news/news-details/2024/Supermicro-Announces-Completion-of-Review-by-Independent-Special-Committee/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">has concluded</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742459-super-micro-computer-smci-measuring-risks-hold-for-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:50:54"}, {"id": "4742453", "title": "Caleres: Margins Are Returning To The Mean As Warned, Still A Hold", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"lots of different shoes stacked in hallway\" data-id=\"82567332\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Martin Poole</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Caleres, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CAL\" title=\"Caleres, Inc.\">CAL</a></span>) presented its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4365344-caleres-non-gaap-eps-of-1_23-misses-0_12-revenue-of-740_94m-misses-10_42m\">Q3 2024 results</a>, which were not bad, with revenues growing on a comparable basis in both the retail and the wholesale branded sector, and operating margins sustained well despite lower absolute</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742453-caleres-margins-are-returning-to-the-mean-as-warned-still-a-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:35:38"}, {"id": "4742448", "title": "UniCredit: Will It Be The Next Leading EU Bank?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Unicredit Tower skyscraper in Milan\" data-id=\"1014081722\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Cineberg</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Here at the Lab, we have good coverage of EU financial institutions. This year, the sector has already delivered a 31% total return, and the banking industry still trades at a 20% discount to long-run P/E multiple and a 47% discount to the broader market. This</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742448-unicredit-stock-will-it-be-next-leading-eu-bank", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:15:49"}, {"id": "4742445", "title": "Signet: It Has Been Great For Trading, But Not This Time", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stop sign\" data-id=\"157640177\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4368px\" height=\"2912px\" srcset=\"https://stat